1145
01:39:22,665 --> 01:39:24,338
Erik!

1146
01:40:09,128 --> 01:40:09,879
Storm !

1147
01:40:29,190 --> 01:40:30,612
Ayo ayo!

1148
01:40:46,707 --> 01:40:47,674
Ayo, ayo!

1149
01:40:47,833 --> 01:40:49,255
Beri peringatan DEFCON 3.

1150
01:40:49,418 --> 01:40:50,510
Pak Presiden, situasi berbahaya.

1151
01:40:50,670 --> 01:40:52,047
Bagaimana pertahanan udara kita?

1152
01:40:52,213 --> 01:40:53,430
Seluruh pertahanan udara siap.

1153
01:40:53,589 --> 01:40:54,932
Apa yang terjadi?

1154
01:40:55,091 --> 01:40:56,058
Akan kubereskan.

1155
01:40:56,217 --> 01:40:57,218
Kau bilang begitu sebelumnya.

1156
01:40:57,385 --> 01:40:58,557
Aku ingin buat pernyataan.

1157
01:40:58,719 --> 01:41:01,472
Kini seluruh dunia tahu kita
tak bisa melindungi mereka.

1158
01:41:01,639 --> 01:41:02,640
Akan kubereskan.

1159
01:41:02,807 --> 01:41:04,559
Sebaiknya begitu.

1160
01:42:16,047 --> 01:42:17,048
Charles!

1161
01:43:06,097 --> 01:43:07,815
Semua baik - baik saja?

1162
01:43:41,674 --> 01:43:42,641
Tidak!

1163
01:43:46,554 --> 01:43:47,555
Di belakangmu!

1164
01:44:32,141 --> 01:44:33,438
Sekarang!

1165
01:44:56,791 --> 01:44:59,385
Mungkin aku tak boleh
menanyakan ini...,

1166
01:44:59,877 --> 01:45:02,471
Tapi apa aku selamat
di masa depan?

1167
01:45:02,922 --> 01:45:03,798
Tidak.

1168
01:45:06,008 --> 01:45:07,305
Tapi kita bisa mengubah itu.

1169
01:45:07,468 --> 01:45:09,061
Benar?

1170
01:45:19,647 --> 01:45:21,274
Berfungsilah sesuai rancanganmu.

1171
01:45:22,358 --> 01:45:23,701
Mutan.

1172
01:45:30,491 --> 01:45:31,993
Kau di mana?

1173
01:45:49,385 --> 01:45:50,853
Biar kutangani! Pergilah!

1174
01:46:33,596 --> 01:46:35,223
Ya Tuhan.

1175
01:46:51,155 --> 01:46:53,328
Kau bukan lagi yang
bisa bertahan.

1176
01:47:35,866 --> 01:47:37,118
Salah satu dari mereka di sini.

1177
01:47:39,745 --> 01:47:41,463
Tidak! Jangan dibunuh!

1178
01:47:42,206 --> 01:47:43,173
Aku butuh dia hidup - hidup.

1179
01:47:56,720 --> 01:47:58,347
Apa yang terjadi?

1180
01:49:06,081 --> 01:49:08,300
Kalian ciptakan senjata ini
untuk membunuh kami.

1181
01:49:09,251 --> 01:49:10,423
Kenapa?

1182
01:49:14,548 --> 01:49:17,267
<i>Karena kalian takut
pada anugerah kami.</i>

1183
01:49:18,177 --> 01:49:20,680
<i>Karena kami berbeda.</i>

1184
01:49:22,139 --> 01:49:25,439
<i>Manusia selalu takut
pada hal yang berbeda.</i>

1185
01:49:25,893 --> 01:49:27,270
<i>Kukatakan pada kalian...</i>

1186
01:49:27,478 --> 01:49:28,855
...pada dunia...

1187
01:49:29,855 --> 01:49:32,028
...kalian benar takut pada kami.

1188
01:49:32,441 --> 01:49:34,159
<i>Kamilah masa depan.</i>

1189
01:49:34,860 --> 01:49:37,534
<i>Kamilah yang akan
mewarisi dunia ini.</i>

1190
01:49:37,821 --> 01:49:40,415
Siapa pun yang menghalangi kami...

1191
01:49:40,574 --> 01:49:42,542
...akan menerima akibat yang
sama dengan orang - orang...

1192
01:49:42,701 --> 01:49:44,044
...yang ada di hadapan kalian.

1193
01:49:51,293 --> 01:49:53,921
<i>Hari ini harusnya untuk
memamerkan kekuatan kalian.</i>

1194
01:49:54,671 --> 01:49:56,765
Namun kuberi
sekilas gambaran...

1195
01:49:56,924 --> 01:50:00,394
<i>...kehancuran yang bisa dibuat
kaumku pada kalian.</i>

1196
01:50:09,645 --> 01:50:11,818
<i>Biarlah ini jadi
peringatan bagi dunia.</i>

1197
01:50:12,523 --> 01:50:15,322
<i>Dan pada saudara - saudari
Mutanku di luar sana...,</i>

1198
01:50:16,068 --> 01:50:17,536
<i>Kukatakan ini.</i>

1199
01:50:18,237 --> 01:50:19,910
<i>Tak perlu lagi bersembunyi.</i>

1200
01:50:20,072 --> 01:50:21,949
<i>Tak ada lagi penderitaan.</i>

1201
01:50:22,783 --> 01:50:25,161
Kalian telah hidup
dalam bayang - bayang...

1202
01:50:25,327 --> 01:50:28,126
<i>...rasa malu dan takut
terlalu lama. Keluarlah.</i>

1203
01:50:29,665 --> 01:50:30,666
<i>Bergabunglah denganku.</i>

1204
01:50:30,833 --> 01:50:34,337
<i>Berperang bersama dalam
persaudaraan kaum kita.</i>

1205
01:50:34,962 --> 01:50:36,635
Hari esok yang baru...

1206
01:50:37,840 --> 01:50:39,592
...yang dimulai hari ini.

1207
01:50:46,849 --> 01:50:48,692
<i>Tahun - tahun itu terbuang...</i>

1208
01:50:48,851 --> 01:50:50,853
...untuk saling berkelahi, Charles.

1209
01:50:54,398 --> 01:50:58,028
Agar waktu berharga itu kembali.

1210
01:51:36,773 --> 01:51:37,899
Pak Presiden.
/ Mundur.

1211
01:51:38,066 --> 01:51:39,943
Kubilang, mundur!

1212
01:51:41,778 --> 01:51:43,451
Kau mau buat pernyataan?

1213
01:51:43,906 --> 01:51:45,658
Bunuh aku. Baik.

1214
01:51:45,824 --> 01:51:47,792
Tapi bebaskan yang lain.

1215
01:52:00,422 --> 01:52:02,424
Sangat heroik, Pak Presiden.

1216
01:52:03,342 --> 01:52:04,343
Tapi kau tak berniat...

1217
01:52:04,509 --> 01:52:06,762
...untuk menyisakan kami.

1218
01:52:07,179 --> 01:52:10,558
Masa depan kaum kami
dimulai sekarang.

1219
01:52:15,145 --> 01:52:16,146
Mutan.

1220
01:52:20,108 --> 01:52:21,200
Mutan.

1221
01:52:46,093 --> 01:52:47,390
Dulu kau penembak yang baik.

1222
01:52:47,552 --> 01:52:48,428
Percayalah, aku masih lihai.

1223
01:53:02,401 --> 01:53:03,948
Keluar dari kepalaku, Charles!

1224
01:53:04,111 --> 01:53:05,613
Raven.

1225
01:53:05,779 --> 01:53:07,656
Tolonglah, jangan buat
kita jadi jahat hari ini.

1226
01:53:07,864 --> 01:53:09,707
Lihat sekelilingmu.
Kita sudah jahat.

1227
01:53:10,200 --> 01:53:11,918
Tidak semua.

1228
01:53:12,744 --> 01:53:14,997
Yang kau lakukan sejauh ini...

1229
01:53:15,163 --> 01:53:16,790
...ialah menyelamatkan
orang - orang ini.

1230
01:53:17,749 --> 01:53:20,343
Kau bisa menunjukkan mereka
jalan yang lebih baik.

1231
01:53:24,006 --> 01:53:25,053
Lumpuhkan dia, Charles.

1232
01:53:27,676 --> 01:53:31,271
Kucoba mengendalikanmu
sejak pertama kita berjumpa...

1233
01:53:31,680 --> 01:53:33,682
...dan lihat akibatnya.

1234
01:53:35,809 --> 01:53:38,358
Semua yang terjadi sekarang...

1235
01:53:39,271 --> 01:53:41,490
...ada di tanganmu.

1236
01:53:45,527 --> 01:53:48,280
Aku percaya padamu, Raven.

1237
01:55:27,003 --> 01:55:29,131
Dia milikmu, Charles.

1238
01:55:56,700 --> 01:55:59,328
Jika kau biarkan mereka
menangkapku, aku pasti mati.

1239
01:55:59,494 --> 01:56:00,871
Kau tahu itu.

1240
01:56:01,538 --> 01:56:02,755
Aku tahu.

1241
01:56:05,125 --> 01:56:06,798
Selamat tinggal, teman lama.

1242
01:56:09,421 --> 01:56:11,298
Selamat tinggal, Erik.

1243
01:56:44,706 --> 01:56:46,708
Kau yakin mau melepas mereka?

1244
01:56:47,667 --> 01:56:49,044
Ya.

1245
01:56:49,628 --> 01:56:51,380
Aku punya harapan
untuk mereka.

1246
01:56:52,547 --> 01:56:56,552
Akan ada waktunya, Hank,
saat kita semua akan bekerja sama.

1247
01:57:00,430 --> 01:57:02,398
Bagaimana dengan Logan?

1248
01:58:18,008 --> 01:58:21,182
Buckminster Fuller adalah
contoh arsitek bagus...

1249
01:58:21,344 --> 01:58:25,565
...yang idenya sangat mirip
dengan khayalan masa depan.

1250
01:58:31,896 --> 01:58:34,570
Selamat pagi, Logan.
Kau bangun siang.

1251
01:58:44,701 --> 01:58:46,044
Selamat menikmati makan siang.

1252
01:58:46,202 --> 01:58:47,419
Kerjamu baik.

1253
01:58:47,746 --> 01:58:49,089
Sangat baik.

1254
01:58:49,998 --> 01:58:51,215
Storm.

1255
01:59:22,656 --> 01:59:23,748
Jean.

1256
01:59:25,158 --> 01:59:26,125
Hei, Logan.

1257
01:59:27,035 --> 01:59:28,161
Jean.

1258
01:59:28,870 --> 01:59:30,588
Kau baik - baik saja?

1259
01:59:32,290 --> 01:59:33,291
Kau di sini.

1260
01:59:34,376 --> 01:59:36,424
Seharusnya aku di mana?

1261
01:59:38,713 --> 01:59:39,760
Wow.

1262
01:59:40,548 --> 01:59:42,471
Hati - hati, Sobat.

1263
01:59:44,052 --> 01:59:46,601
Ada yang tak berubah.

1264
01:59:47,972 --> 01:59:49,599
Senang melihatmu, Scott.

1265
01:59:51,393 --> 01:59:52,394
Ya.

1266
01:59:52,686 --> 01:59:53,858
Sampai nanti, Jean.

1267
01:59:57,982 --> 01:59:59,575
Profesor.

1268
02:00:00,276 --> 02:00:03,075
Logan, semua baik saja?

1269
02:00:06,157 --> 02:00:07,374
Ya.

1270
02:00:08,702 --> 02:00:10,545
Ya, kurasa.

1271
02:00:27,095 --> 02:00:27,937
Kau berhasil.

1272
02:00:28,638 --> 02:00:29,560
Berhasil apa?

1273
02:00:29,723 --> 02:00:31,691
Logan, bukankah kau
harus mengajar kelas?

1274
02:00:32,350 --> 02:00:34,068
Mengajar kelas?

1275
02:00:35,103 --> 02:00:36,150
Sejarah.

1276
02:00:36,896 --> 02:00:37,943
Sejarah?

1277
02:00:39,232 --> 02:00:40,905
Sebenarnya, aku butuh bantuan
tentang sejarah.

1278
02:00:41,359 --> 02:00:43,157
Bantuan apa?

1279
02:00:43,319 --> 02:00:47,244
Semua yang terjadi setelah 1973.

1280
02:00:51,077 --> 02:00:54,581
Sejarah yang kutahu
sedikit berbeda.

1281
02:00:55,790 --> 02:00:58,259
Selamat datang kembali.

1282
02:01:00,253 --> 02:01:01,880
Senang melihatmu, Charles.

1283
02:01:03,298 --> 02:01:05,141
Senang melihat semua orang.

1284
02:01:05,300 --> 02:01:06,301
Yah...

1285
02:01:07,385 --> 02:01:09,604
Aku harus menepati janjiku.

1286
02:01:10,722 --> 02:01:14,022
Kau dan aku banyak
yang perlu dibicarakan.

1287
02:01:14,893 --> 02:01:15,894
Ya.

1288
02:01:19,981 --> 02:01:22,484
Apa yang terakhir kau ingat?

1289
02:01:27,197 --> 02:01:28,915
Tenggelam.

1290
02:01:37,665 --> 02:01:38,917
<i>Masa lalu.</i>

1291
02:01:40,001 --> 02:01:41,093
<i>Dunia baru...</i>

1292
02:01:41,252 --> 02:01:43,050
<i>...dan tak menentu.</i>

1293
02:01:54,432 --> 02:01:56,730
<i>Dunia dengan kemungkinan
tanpa batas.</i>

1294
02:01:56,893 --> 02:01:58,895
Mutan Selamatkan Presiden dan
Kabinet Program Sentinel Dibatalkan

1295
02:01:59,062 --> 02:02:00,109
Trask Ditahan Karena
Menjual Rahasia Militer

1296
02:02:00,188 --> 02:02:01,610
<i>Dan akibat tak terbatas.</i>

1297
02:02:03,441 --> 02:02:04,408
Yang benar saja.

1298
02:02:04,567 --> 02:02:06,035
Dia masih hidup!

1299
02:02:10,406 --> 02:02:13,125
<i>Pilihan tanpa batas
menentukan takdir kita.</i>

1300
02:02:14,077 --> 02:02:16,546
<i>Setiap pilihan,
setiap peristiwa...</i>

1301
02:02:16,704 --> 02:02:18,798
<i>...adalah riak di sungai waktu.</i>

1302
02:02:19,457 --> 02:02:21,801
Kita apakan dia, Mayor Stryker?

1303
02:02:21,960 --> 02:02:23,758
<i>Riak yang cukup...</i>

1304
02:02:23,920 --> 02:02:26,514
<i>...untuk mengubah
air pasang.</i>

1305
02:02:26,673 --> 02:02:27,765
Biar kuurus dia.

1306
02:02:27,924 --> 02:02:31,849
<i>Karena masa depan
belumlah ditentukan.</i>

